Master-Child Auto Copy Trading: A Complete Setup Guide

Here is an extensive, easy-to-follow setup procedure for platforms like Zerodha, Alice Blue, MT4, MT5, and so on.

1. Opt for a Copy Trading Software That Is Reliable

Go for a copy trading solution that is both reputable and stable. The most popular choices are:

Combiz Services Pvt Ltd (Highly Recommended)

Other MT4/MT5 trade copiers

